data.description: This exquisite single-story residence is nestled in the charming Vintage Green Valley enclave. This stunning property boasts a beautiful pool, relaxing spa, and a spacious 3-car garage. Inside, you'll find a wealth of elegant features, including timeless plantation shutters gracing every window and inviting hardwood floors that flow throughout. The kitchen showcases beautiful granite countertops, complemented by an abundance of rich maple cabinets, creating an ideal culinary space. The family room is a cozy retreat, complete with a convenient wet bar and a warming fireplace, perfect for gathering and making lasting memories. Large primary bedroom with an ensuite that feature double sinks, a large bathtub and a separate shower. This home is a true gem, offering comfort, style, and a tranquil lifestyle in a coveted community.
